data.description: EXPECT TO BE IMPRESSED - SO MANY UPDATES! Welcome to 20 Jason Dr / great location / corner ranch / 3 bedrooms / 3 baths! Living room with vaulted ceiling & lots of natural light. Kitchen features plenty of new shaker cabinets, quartz counters, pantry cabinet, breakfast area, plus all stainless appliance stay. Primary bedroom suite includes a private 3/4 bath & walk in closet. 2 additional bedrooms and full main bath complete main level. Let's go downstairs - Huge family room, office and 1/2 bath. Great storage / utility room. You'll love the backyard, vinyl fence & brand new deck. Full list of updates provided on MLS - be sure to ask your agent. Just to mention a few - Roof, siding, windows, kitchen, all baths, HVAC, interior & exterior doors, flooring on both levels, deck and more. 2 car attached garage & great curb appeal. Just move in & call it HOME! Buyer's to verify ask MLS data, including but not limited, to square footage, measurements, taxes, exemptions, lot size, schools, etc.
